-cw:1170px" class="sc-cqJhZP gRKDwp"><div class="sc-efQSVx kdrjec pf-24_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:0px;--s-sm:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-eySxxw fIKYYX pf-25_"><p class="sc-dMOJrz cGFGtP pf-26_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-bjztik hIbmEr pf-28_">Many people shy away from <a href="https://www.cliphair.co.uk/" target="_blank">hair extensions</a> as they still think of them as the type that is glued into your hair. These can cause damage and make it difficult to alter your style. With <a href="https://www.cliphair.co.uk/collections/clip-in-hair-extensions" target="_blank">Clip in hair extensions</a>, you can adapt your style to go with your mood as they can be attached and removed within minutes.
<br>
<br>Also gone are the days when clip in hair extensions could not be altered or groomed. Or if they did they would lose some of their quality. At Clip Hair our real hair extensions can be curled, straightened, crimped and styled. They can even be coloured if desired.<br><p> </p></span></p></div></div></div><div class="sc-efQSVx kdrjec pf-29_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:0px;--s-sm:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-eySxxw fIKYYX pf-30_"><h2 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-eJwWfJ hSzDKM pf-31_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-bjztik hIbmEr pf-33_">Your Cliphair extensions are real human hair extensions. They should be treated with the same care.</span></h2></div></div></div><div class="sc-efQSVx kdrjec pf-34_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:0px;--s-sm:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-eySxxw fIKYYX pf-35_"><p class="sc-dMOJrz cGFGtP pf-36_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-bjztik hIbmEr pf-38_">In terms of looking after your extensions, the simple rule is to remember that these are human hair extensions, so treat them as you would your real hair. You can <a href="https://www.cliphair.co.uk/products/cliphair-shampoo-conditioner" target="_blank">shampoo, condition</a> and blow dry just as you would your own hair, so you do not need to spend money on fake hair products and worry about doing something wrong.<br><p> </p></span></p><p class="sc-dMOJrz cGFGtP pf-39_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-bjztik hIbmEr pf-41_">In a similar way, treat your clip in hair extensions with the same respect you would your own head of hair. You wouldn’t drag a brush through your own wet hair, or burn it with too hot styling appliances, so give the real <a href="https://www.cliphair.co.uk/blogs/hair-blog/how-to-look-after-hair-extensions-ultimate-care-guide" target="_blank">hair extensions the love and care</a> they deserve.<br><p> </p></span></p><h2 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-eJwWfJ hSzDKM pf-42_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-bjztik hIbmEr pf-44_">Tips and tricks on how to care for your real human hair extensions</span></h2><p class="sc-dMOJrz cGFGtP pf-45_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-bjztik hIbmEr pf-47_">1) Don't sleep with your clip in hair extensions. Always make sure to take them off before going to bed. <br>2) Be gentle while brushing your extensions.<br>3) Use heating tools at a minimum level<br>4) Store them properly to prevent tangling<br>5) Keep them moisturised. <br>6) If you are using hair spray, make sure to wash them off properly.<br>7) Let it air dry for a longer life span<br><p> </p></span></p></div></div></div></div></div><div data-section-id="pf-ca45" data-pf-type="Section" class="sc-jNHqnW kXSKNz pf-48_"><div style="--cw:1170px" class="sc-cqJhZP gRKDwp"><div class="sc-efQSVx kdrjec pf-49_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-eySxxw fIKYYX pf-50_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-eJwWfJ hSzDKM pf-51_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-bjztik hIbmEr pf-53_"><span style="font-weight: normal;">For more information about hair extensions,why not&nbsp;</span><a href="https://www.cliphair.co.uk/pages/colour-matching-service" target="_self" style="font-weight: normal;">book a free colour matching</a> <br><span style="font-weight: normal;">with our hair experts?&nbsp;</span>We are here to help.</span></h3><div data-slider="{'slidesToShow':{'all':3,'laptop':3,'tablet':2,'mobile':1},'slidesToScroll':{'all':1,'laptop':1,'tablet':1,'mobile':1},'loop':false,'autoPlay':false,'autoPlayDelay':3000,'pauseOnHover':false,'id':'6201afce-7c09-40ca-85b4-01fb66fb8818'}" class="sc-hiCibw dJQIUB pf-54_ glider-n-1" style="visibility:hidden;height:380px" data-pf-type="Slider"><div